    "is_public": true,
    "title": "Courgette, Herb & Egg Frittata",
    "description": "Ingredients: 3 courgettes (Green Valley), 6 eggs (Sunny Meadow), handful of fresh basil and parsley (Green Valley), 50 g mature cheddar (Sunny Meadow), salt & pepper.\n\nSlice and fry courgettes until golden. Beat eggs, stir in herbs and cheese. Pour over courgettes in an ovenproof pan. Cook on hob 3 min then finish under a hot grill for 5 min. Serves 3ÔÇô4.",
    "created_at": "2026-04-23T23:49:01.377Z"
  }
